ygData.messageBody:
OK I hit 20 and I was in unrest loading up on full bronze armour, ( i am
dwarf ), and most things are blue, or red. Like Dry bones are good to kill
but if anything else comes I got to run or get help. Everything else is too
physco. Where is a good fighting area for level 20 and has descent money?
